@startuml
title Module Pipeline - Ontology and Taxonomy Mapping
top to bottom direction

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Inputs" {
  folder "events (data/exports/events)" as EVTX
  folder "relations (data/exports/relations)" as RELX
  folder "entities (data/exports/entities)" as ENTX
}

package "src.ontology" {
  component "taxonomy.py" as TAX
}

package "Semantic standards" {
  component "CAMEO / GDELT event taxonomy" as CAMEO
  component "IPTC media topics" as IPTC
  component "OWL-Time temporal concepts" as OWLT
}

package "Consumers" {
  component "event_extractor.py" as EVT
  component "relation_extractor.py" as REL
  component "graph_loader.py" as LOAD
  component "competency_queries.py" as CQ
}

EVTX --> TAX
RELX --> TAX
ENTX --> TAX

TAX --> CAMEO
TAX --> IPTC
TAX --> OWLT

TAX --> EVT
TAX --> REL
TAX --> LOAD
TAX --> CQ

note bottom of TAX
Provides normalized labels and mapping logic used by extraction,
graph materialization, and downstream analytics.
end note

@enduml
